  "stemHtml": "<p>Refer to figures or CAP 698 files 4.8 and 4.9. <br /> \rAn MRJT is scheduled to take-off from the Madrid Airport. Given the following information below, determine the V<strong><sub>1</sub></strong>, V<strong><sub>R</sub></strong> and V<strong><sub>2</sub></strong> take-off speeds.</p>\r\r<p>Airport elevation: 1998 ft <br /> \rOAT: +10\u00b0C <br /> \rActual take-off mass: 62 800 kg <br /> \rFlaps: 15\u00b0 <br /> \rRunway slope: 0.8% down <br /> \rWind component: 5 kt tailwind</p>",
  "options": {
    "a": "<p>V<sub>1</sub> = 142 kt, V<sub>R</sub> = 143 kt and V<sub>2</sub> = 149 kt</p>",
    "b": "<p>V<sub>1</sub> = 143 kt, V<sub>R</sub> = 146 kt and V<sub>2</sub> = 151 kt</p>",
    "c": "<p>V<sub>1</sub> = 136 kt, V<sub>R</sub> = 140 kt and V<sub>2</sub> = 151 kt</p>",
    "d": "<p>V<sub>1</sub> = 140 kt, V<sub>R</sub> = 143 kt and V<sub>2</sub> = 149 kt</p>"
  },
  "correctOption": "d",
